response.original_title: NJPW Road To Power Struggle 2017: Day 4
response.overview: On October 22, 2017, New Sunpia Tochigi in Kanuma hosted Day 4 of NJPW Road To Power Struggle 2017.  The main event featured Los Ingobernables de Japon (BUSHI, EVIL, Hiromu Takahashi, SANADA & Tetsuya Naito) vs CHAOS (Kazuchika Okada, Rocky Romero, SHO, YOH & YOSHI-HASHI).  The card also featured David Finlay, Juice Robinson & Kota Ibushi vs Hiroshi Tanahashi, Katsuya Kitamura & Togi Makabe.  Other wrestlers on the show include Ren Narita, Tetsuhiro Yagi and more!
response.title: NJPW Road To Power Struggle 2017: Day 4
